metadata.name: Amanda
metadata.description: Amanda is the first sister. She loves pistachios and while he was eating pistachios, her sister threw an ice cream ball at him out of mischief. In that hot weather, not only was she not angry with his sister, but she was very happy because she came up with the idea of making cool ice cream hats. She was the one who made the first pistachio-flavored ice cream hat to get rid of the heat.
